&lt;Noranda Inc> said it agreed to buy aninitial 1,000,501 treasury shares of &lt;Sanivan Group Inc> at5.25 dlrs per share.    Noranda also has an option until June 30, 1988, to acquirean additional 1,000,501 Sanivan treasury shares at 5.75 dlrsper share.    Sanivan is the largest hazardous waste management companyin Canada. Reuter&#3;